							<h1 class="title">Aluminum Bed Frame</h1>
														
														
							<div id="_mcePaste"><strong>Project</strong>:Â Aluminum Bed Frame</div>
<div id="_mcePaste"><strong>Description</strong>: Brushed aluminum frame with maple or bamboo headboard and footboard, locking rubber wheels optional. Headboard adjusts to different mattress thicknesses. Various sizes and trundle versions.</div>
<div id="_mcePaste"><strong>Client</strong>: Abraxas Arts, Inc.</div>
<div id="_mcePaste"><strong>Year</strong>: 1996</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-988" title="bed.atraxia.bamboo.aluminum.1" src="http://74.220.215.203/~glendong/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/bed.atraxia.bamboo.aluminum.1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" /></p>
